import { Box, Button, Header, Heading, Text, Tab, Tabs } from 'grommet';
import { Hpe } from 'grommet-icons';
import React from 'react';


function TabsForm() {

    return(
        <>
        <Header background="brand">
            <Box direction="row" gap="small" pad="medium">
                <Hpe color="White"/>
                <Text weight="bold">HPE</Text>
                <Text>Console</Text>
            </Box>
        </Header>
        <Heading>Customs Annexure</Heading>

        <Box alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'medium' }} pad="large">
            <Box direction="row" alignSelf="start" gap="small">
                <Button primary label="ClickMe" href="/Component/TabsFoem2" size="small"/>
            </Box>
            <Box direction="row" alignSelf="center"  border={{ color: 'brand', size: 'medium' }} pad="medium"> 
                <Tabs>
                    <Tab title="Procurement Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 1</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Forwarder Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 2</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="CHA Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 3</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Supplier & Product Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 4</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Customs Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 5</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Invoice Remittance Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 6</Box>
                    </Tab>
                    <Tab title="Asset-grave Section">
                        <Box pad="medium">Device Name 7</Box>
                    </Tab>
                </Tabs>
            </Box>
        </Box>
        </>
    );
}

export default TabsForm;
